videos.description: Grayson Allen disrupts the Syracuse offense with a steal and has an open lane for the jam.
videos.headline: Duke off to hot start with Allen steal and slam

videos.description: Grayson Allen connects with Marvin Bagley III twice for huge alley-oops to get the "Cameron Crazies" on their feet.
videos.headline: Allen hits Bagley III with two alley-oops

videos.description: Marvin Bagley III uses two great feeds from Wendell Carter Jr. to get to the bucket for big-time slams.
videos.headline: Big man to big man, Carter to Bagley III for two huge jams

videos.description: Marques Bolden gets the feed down low and rises up for a huge two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Bolden is dubbed 'mayor' of jam city

videos.description: Wendell Carter Jr. rises up to grab the alley-oop pass from Grayson Allen for another two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Carter Jr.'s jam has the 'crazies' dancing in the aisles

videos.description: Marvin Bagley III wanted to come out aggressive in his return from injury and he did just that, dropping 19 points.
videos.headline: Bagley III: 'I'm blessed to be back out'

videos.description: The Blue Devils hold Syracuse to 44 points and Marvin Bagley III impresses in his return from injury as Duke defeats Syracuse.
videos.headline: Duke's defense shines in win over Syracuse

videos.description: Wendell Carter Jr. and Marvin Bagley III combine for more than half of the No. 5 Blue Devils' points as they stifle the Orange 60-44.
videos.headline: Duke rolls behind freshmen bigs
